title: #120 - Ethan Prochnik, Lorenzo Hodges, & ME
description: Emmy Award winning Producer Ethan Prochnik, my old roomate Lorenzo Hodges & I hang outside the Mancave have some beers and talk about Ethans work on the Deadliest Catch, Afghanistan, and his extensive reasearch & experience with Ayahuasca.
